OL,3,CMore Scots business owners anticipate
OL,4,Chigher turnover in 2025, poll suggests
OL,6,FAlmost three quarters of Scottish
OL,7,Fbusinesses are confident about their
OL,8,Fprospects next year, a survey has
OL,9,Fsuggested.
OL,11,FThe Bank of Scotland's business
OL,12,Fbarometer poll showed 73% of Scottish
OL,13,Fbusinesses expect to see turnover
OL,14,Fincrease in 2025, up from 60% polled
OL,15,Fin 2023.
OL,17,FAlmost a quarter (23%) of businesses
OL,18,Fexpect to see their revenue rise by
OL,19,Fbetween six and 10% over the next 12
OL,20,Fmonths, with just over a fifth (21%)
OL,21,Fexpecting it to grow by even more.
