OL,6,FThe poll found that 70% of businesses
OL,7,Fwere confident they would become more
OL,8,Fprofitable in 2025, a two per cent
OL,9,Fincrease when compared with the
OL,10,Fprevious year.
OL,12,FRevenue and profitability growth was
OL,13,Ffirms' top priority at 52%, though 40%
OL,14,Fsaid they will be targeting improved
OL,15,Fproductivity, and the same proportion
OL,16,Fsaid they will be aiming to enhance
OL,17,Ftheir technology ` such as automation
OL,18,For AI ` or upskill their staff (both
OL,19,F29%).
