OL,3,CMore Scots business owners anticipate
OL,4,Chigher turnover in 2025, poll suggests
OL,6,FMartyn Kendrick, Scotland director at
OL,7,FBank of Scotland commercial banking,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Scottish businesses are looking
OL,9,Fahead to 2025 with stronger growth
OL,10,Fexpectations, and setting out clear
OL,11,Fplans to drive this expansion through
OL,12,Finvestments in new technology, new
OL,13,Fmarkets and their own teams.
OL,15,F"As we enter the new year, we'll
OL,16,Fcontinue to by their side to help them
OL,17,Fpursue their ambitions and seize all
OL,18,Fopportunities that lie ahead."
